Find over 70 different weapons and 18 new utilities to fend off the Infected and hostile players in this open world survival shooter! Use a variety of cars, trucks, and boats to explore a diverse archipelago with up to five players in a group, or on your own. Unlock unique cosmetics by finding secret locations, special Boss Infected, and random events like helicopter crash sites! VIP servers are available for FREE and allow players to have custom matches on a variety of maps! We will add more maps and expand on VIP servers in the future.

Apocalypse Rising 2 is an Open Alpha! We have plans to release a completely new map in the future, as well as many features and improvements.
